{"tid":476403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[發動技能][求救] 雀bb高處墮下","createTime":"2017-11-22T03:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T03:07:29.000Z","uid":34515,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"023fe24a46f46bc9ac073a7ddfe4c02b98eee158","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:07:14.000Z","msg":"現附上bb圖數張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望有心人指點<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/105812_fe4839b74810218aa243439ee6e614b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F105812_fe4839b74810218aa243439ee6e614b2.jpg&h=59793f89&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/105829_d155568f501b744cf7dcb27db60e4d93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F105829_d155568f501b744cf7dcb27db60e4d93.jpg&h=4dac591c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/105838_011ee48b0b0d9a73800aec6c177523f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F105838_011ee48b0b0d9a73800aec6c177523f3.jpg&h=38457dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/105844_7b1f17515ea8265c045c35e199e95322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F105844_7b1f17515ea8265c045c35e199e95322.jpg&h=7f3753ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/105849_5b7d693aac8da445b0182a88165a665c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F105849_5b7d693aac8da445b0182a88165a665c.jpg&h=2d930de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事緣翻屋企撘巴士落車嗰陣見到路中心有隻嘢<br />\n行過去發現係雀b 望上樹上面3.4米見到有個巢<br />\n本身諗住係附近等下 睇佢老豆老母執唔執返佢<br />\n因為驚有其他雀食佢唔敢行開<br />\n但等多陣之後人有三急所以衝翻屋企去廁所<br />\n去完就跑翻去揾佢 <br />\n冇掂到佢情況之下執咗翻屋企 暫時收留佢<br />\n諗緊點放翻上去因為始終太高<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家想問下有冇巴絲知佢幾大 食得啲咩 點湊佢 同點俾水佢飲 佢毛未生齊飛唔到 好似企到但唔知咁高跌落嚟有冇內傷"},{"pid":"dbfb38a10650c9944fdac863682daedbe11c69f5","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f233c7cf9ce32d590268a4e258e6784fb5e9909","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:08:10.000Z","msg":"唔識都推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2692024ebcad38035f0c4081ab2b2056202ecb","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:08:31.000Z","msg":"頭先開po又冇人理"},{"pid":"ac6588b2ab163e997295bcebab6a48f0a26d58b8","tid":476403,"uid":64849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:08:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85c89c354c6d8a2e498693f251e85054af0b8f66","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"連登冷血無知涼薄"},{"pid":"2edf40a215ff203c386730991e1a5c8c206888d3","tid":476403,"uid":156751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"你執左返去就有你陣味了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11f8ffd393cabf525a202dffb8a6bf67e59e46d","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:11:48.000Z","msg":"幫手推po嘅祝你高大威猛上進有錢了靚仔同大波長腿百年不老又靚女"},{"pid":"437ffa2dac9924c6501ab7a7e9f5025741beb754","tid":476403,"uid":106851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e5bbef96ea7802af746c2984df2683d8f6534dc","tid":47