me":"2017-11-22T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢係咁訓著又起身叫幾下又訓著喺咪肚餓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見唔係呀媽餵可能唔肯食，試多幾次<br />\n注意溫度， 清潔<br />\n搵野遮返佢四週好似響巢咁俾佢覺得安全<br />\n非必要唔好打擾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好！！<br />\n佢起身我就餵佢食少少濕貓糧<br />\n研究緊雀食物"},{"pid":"5fa7da47fa7393e8bf5809c7d71712fc63473da7","tid":476403,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫手推po嘅祝你高大威猛上進有錢了靚仔同大波長腿百年不老又靚女</blockquote><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7a28b7d4fe07a7e2b5ab1404ab1818029e35ee","tid":476403,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"樓主諗住收養?"},{"pid":"37fc9aebc8ad915b64ac72ab8de9a2a642196c86","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"靠連登仔手腳太慢<br />\n唔怪得平時出面瘋傳啲咩永遠冇連登份<br />\n幸得2.3個"},{"pid":"74694137efbdf1c9348619d0ec50050e48573e3d","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靠連登仔手腳太慢<br />\n唔怪得平時出面瘋傳啲咩永遠冇連登份<br />\n幸得2.3個</blockquote><br />\n隻雀起身要餵食㩒錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續<br />\n幸得2.3個好人出手相助<br />\n宜家用借屋企隻貓啲濕貓糧加水餵住先<br />\n同時研究緊雀食嘅人造糧<br />\n宜家30幾度又2.3點時間<br />\n所以地下倒左啲水降下温 驚佢太熱"},{"pid":"55e45b4939fb09921551f9c122490d05e4e77159","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/114629_ee2776ec1166829371a6a6d48aa10fe7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F114629_ee2776ec1166829371a6a6d48aa10fe7.jpg&h=c9682a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/114636_d7bcdc08e6e032514dc54a731b3caefe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F114636_d7bcdc08e6e032514dc54a731b3caefe.jpg&h=0246e813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白色嗰粒係佢第三粒我見到嘅屎<br />\n第一粒喺我用嚟執佢嘅chemistry書封面 已扔<br />\n第二粒喺底 係入屋企後屙嘅<br />\n點解雀bb都咁多屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9075e9bc6824a74550bae0791a75476ec114ac13","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬心地善良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫手推po你都心地善良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3f097b5384cf281e3a25744dfb905c99cc9cf3","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主諗住收養?</blockquote><br />\n養住先 睇屋企人收工有冇方法放翻上去<br />\n問題係驚佢又跳樹"},{"pid":"35a89a1d6bda9f8c9f2f1c841c8c3941060ca2e7","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:51:19.000Z","msg":"暗中一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1bf07daa8f3f8192669424717ac3fa89d4b1f3","tid":476403,"uid":45941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:52:24.000Z","msg":"雀bb好可愛"},{"pid":"613def810e34a07ad9b14055f7e568ed87580206","tid":476403,"uid":34257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/114629_ee2776ec1166829371a6a6d48aa10fe7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F114629_ee2776ec1166829371a6a6d48aa10fe7.jpg&h=c9682a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/114636_d7bcdc08e6e032514dc54a731b3caefe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h