017-11-22T07:50:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>call 愛協or 魚護幫手</blockquote><br />\n外國巴打？<br />\n搵當地動物組織幫手好喎"},{"pid":"fe59b4ff38f7aa37442ad48a2cf77117d008ab5d","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗起以前細個我執左隻雀BB返屋企<br />\n<br />\n果陣佢毛都冇乜 唔好講識飛<br />\n<br />\n點知養左一日比我老豆發現左.....<br />\n<br />\n就話佢識飛 講完就掉左佢落衛街<br />\n<br />\n跟著我即刻跑落樓 就見到隻雀跌死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好慘<br />\n講起 我拎佢翻屋企嗰陣都好怕佢會突然跳起走路<br />\n所以成段路我都保持佢同個地下距離不超過半米<br />\n行到成個呀伯咁"},{"pid":"638ad069c1e8596000a00557ae32dacc215363e8","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>call 愛協or 魚護幫手</blockquote><br />\n外國巴打？<br />\n搵當地動物組織幫手好喎</blockquote><br />\n係呀 有諗過 可能過一兩日拎俾愛協"},{"pid":"52d954e22982045e9a57fc646c608bfeccf22d6c","tid":476403,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>call 愛協or 魚護幫手</blockquote><br />\n外國巴打？<br />\n搵當地動物組織幫手好喎</blockquote><br />\n係呀 有諗過 可能過一兩日拎俾愛協</blockquote><br />\n唔好啦<br />\n愛協會話無人手照顧bb人道毀滅<br />\n你最好養佢個幾星期度佢就會識飛<br />\n之後放左佢啦"},{"pid":"437a9d10c7a7e5ebf2f07a86058a111e0bf9b28c","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"想問雛鳥夜晚係咪唔食嘢㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cf169d31d6962a8ad9db513fd2ad26af38b2aa","tid":476403,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>call 愛協or 魚護幫手</blockquote><br />\n外國巴打？<br />\n搵當地動物組織幫手好喎</blockquote><br />\n係呀 有諗過 可能過一兩日拎俾愛協</blockquote><br />\n唔好啦<br />\n愛協會話無人手照顧bb人道毀滅<br />\n你最好養佢個幾星期度佢就會識飛<br />\n之後放左佢啦</blockquote><br />\n外國愛協都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"09ac4a5215e0d5d824b92bb028d3f093d7bbb8f3","tid":476403,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"雀bb 太花時間 佢地未必肯理"},{"pid":"780f7d09db240cb0fdfaa3df505afe7480c3c3d9","tid":476403,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12edebec3b386ae415306c4bcadf955c2483a92a","tid":476403,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"送去嘉道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雀仔唔係靠嗅覺認仔女 你攞手掂唔使驚會有味而令雀父母唔要佢"},{"pid":"6e177eda37913048d35f5fa66fd3b0f3ad0ef5b2","tid":476403,"uid":132295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0c75895cfc0d0e1bfe56d8561488242f56dedc","tid":476403,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:04:59.000Z","msg":"原來你係外國巴打<br />\n咁仲好 直接送去啲動物機構<br />\n唔好餵麵包 白飯 水果核同皮 部份水果 任何人食嘅加工製品 呢啲上網可以搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />普通雀仔(成鳥)係可以消化部份人食 但幼鳥比較難消化 白飯麵包呢啲係會痴住佢嘅腸胃 然後就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遇到野鳥掉落最好係送番上巢 跟老豆老母學習搵食 生存技能 點都好過跟人<br />\n你好似有養貓?咁盡快送走隻雀 貓始終天性係會獵殺雀仔 野貓家貓都係 除非你可以24小時望住隻雀"},{"pid":"2bd82d46e2d233c4eced82e152d45c9ae5f68acb","tid":476403,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問雛鳥夜晚係咪唔食嘢㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇下佢會唔會半夜隔幾粒鐘就鳩叫<br />\n佢而家識唔識跑/跳/低飛<br />\n我就咁睇佢個大細 應該就已經唔使 or等其他專家解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c498651c563a0e4cb08b74902cec2e4e27dd575f","tid":476403,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:14:37.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"6f78eaeac76e04c719a4eb6a56bcea1c7b4f211e","tid":476403,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問雛鳥夜晚係咪唔食嘢㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔食的<br />\n放暗處會訓覺<br />\n睇住你隻貓呀喂...<br />\n戶外又可能有危險"},{"pid":"2598e847935a7485b7d66830568a8c8d85a3d6c8","tid":476403,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來你係外國巴打<br />\n咁仲好 直接送去啲動物機構<br />\n唔好餵麵包 白飯 水果核同皮 部份水果 任何人食嘅加工製品 呢啲上網可以搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />普通雀仔(成鳥)係可以消化部份人食 但幼鳥比較難消化 白飯麵包呢啲係會痴住佢嘅腸胃 然後就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遇到野鳥掉落最好係送番上巢 跟老豆老母學習搵食 生存技能 點都好過跟人<br />\n你好似有養貓?咁盡快送走隻雀 貓始終天性係會獵殺雀仔 野貓家貓都係 除非你可以24小時望住隻雀</blockquote><br />\n我乜都俾屋企兩隻雀食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfed8b1f2085da992606857133eeed1373c0237","tid":476403,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來你係外國巴打<br />\n咁仲好 直接送去啲動物機構<br />\n唔好餵麵包 白飯 水果核同皮 部份水果 任何人食嘅加工製品 呢啲上網可以搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />普通雀仔(成鳥)係可以消化部份人食 但幼鳥比較難消化 白飯麵包呢啲係會痴住佢嘅腸胃 然後就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遇到野鳥掉落最好係送番上巢 跟老豆老母學習搵食 生存技能 點都好過跟人<br />\n你好似有養貓?咁盡快送走隻雀 貓始終天性係會獵殺雀仔 野貓家貓都係 除非你可以24小時望住隻雀</blockquote><br />\n我乜都俾屋企兩隻雀食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要睇隻雀嘅年齡 身體狀況<br />\n幼鳥最好就唔好食啦 佢地嘅生命好脆弱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fb啲雀仔group成日有人亂餵野食比bb雀之後隻雀死咗就po上網取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}